      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. Applicant must be registered as an unorganized worker in any district of the state. \n1. Applicant must be between the ages of 18 and 60. \n1. Unorganized workers who are receiving benefits from any other parallel scheme of the State Government are not eligible for the scheme.\n\n",
